jhelp.util.list

Class ListFromArray<TYPE>

  • java.lang.Object
    • jhelp.util.list.ListFromArray<TYPE>
  • Type Parameters:
    TYPE - Type of the element in the array
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<TYPE>, java.util.Collection<TYPE>, java.util.List<TYPE>

    public class ListFromArray<TYPE>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.List<TYPE>
    List based on a fix array.
    If an element change from this list, it is also modified to the linked array.
    This ist have some restriction, you can't add or remove element from it. But its possible to read/modfy and element
    Author:
    JHelp
